conversation.label: Time:
conversation.name: Time
conversation.phrase: How comfortable are you with change and mortality?

conversation.label: Space:
conversation.name: Space
conversation.phrase: If you could take a one-way trip to a planet that was inhabited (has sentient life) but unexplored by mankind , would you do it and why or why not?

conversation.label: Void:
conversation.name: Void
conversation.phrase: If you could erase all memories of your own mistakes (including what you learned from them) would you choose to do so and why/ why not?

conversation.label: Light:
conversation.name: Light
conversation.phrase: What sort of fortune do you seek most? (great wealth, great fame, great luck with love, etc.)

conversation.label: Mind:
conversation.name: Mind
conversation.phrase: You have the ability to read and manipulate the thoughts of others, how do you use this power if you choose to use it at all?

conversation.label: Heart:
conversation.name: Heart
conversation.phrase: Describe someone you believe you would be perfectly romantically compatible with:

conversation.label: Rage:
conversation.name: Rage
conversation.phrase: You have been deeply wronged, to what extent do you seek out revenge?

conversation.label: Hope:
conversation.name: Hope
conversation.phrase: In fifty years, what progress do you most hope the world will make?

conversation.label: Doom:
conversation.name: Doom
conversation.phrase: You know with full certainty your friends are all going to die violently and soon. You cannot stop this. Do you inform them, or keep quiet?

conversation.label: Life:
conversation.name: Life
conversation.phrase: Would you prefer to have unconditional immortality, or the ability to resurrect a lost loved one once (they come back healthy, but you must outlive them to resurrect them, you can choose to do this at any time through your life).

conversation.label: Blood:
conversation.name: Blood
conversation.phrase: Would you give up your personal freedom for the greater good of your family and friends?

conversation.label: Breath:
conversation.name: Breath
conversation.phrase: You're given the opportunity to receive what you wish for most, but you must abandon everyone you care about to get it. You will never see or hear from them again. Do you take the offer?
